# FSU4C does not use local environment variables for secrets.
# All credentials are loaded from GCP Secret Manager at runtime.
#
# Required secrets in project chimera-v4:
#
#   fsu4c-chimera-api-key      Master API key for the X-Chimera-API-Key header
#   chat-oauth-credentials     Google OAuth client JSON {client_id, client_secret, token_uri}
#   chat-token                 Google OAuth token JSON {token, refresh_token, token_uri}
#
# The service account (fsu4c-runner@chimera-v4.iam.gserviceaccount.com) must have:
#   roles/secretmanager.secretAccessor
#   roles/datastore.user
#   roles/storage.objectAdmin
#   roles/pubsub.subscriber
#   roles/logging.logWriter
